WEBVTT

00:07.400 --> 00:09.038
I don't like it.

00:09.073 --> 00:10.585
You oughta be wearing a wire.

00:10.620 --> 00:12.395
Oh. Listen, Leland,

00:12.430 --> 00:14.363
we don't even know what he's got.

00:14.398 --> 00:16.937
Well, look, maybe I should
hang and watch your back.

00:16.972 --> 00:18.090
Oh, come on.

00:18.125 --> 00:19.956
You worry too much. You always did.

00:19.991 --> 00:22.766
Leland, go home. Get some sleep.

00:22.801 --> 00:23.916
Past your bedtime.

00:23.951 --> 00:25.411
Look, Adam, could you do me a favor?

00:25.446 --> 00:26.069
Yeah?

00:26.104 --> 00:29.069
When we're in public,
you call me Captain, okay?

00:29.488 --> 00:32.488
Oh, I'm sorry, Captain.

00:32.972 --> 00:35.972
Still can't say it without laughing.

